description:
Delio is a "blockchain platform to build and operate your own token ecosytem" based on the commercial payment token, "SSC" and "DaaS".

SSC stands for Stable Stake Coin which is a decentralized stable coin specifically designed for commercial payment.

DaaS stands for Delio As A Service which is a blockchain solution enabling companies to issue and operate their own tokens on a ASP method.
name: Delio
